Package medit

Main Application package

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutBox
    AboutBox is dialog containing information about MEdit.
    CommandOutputDialog
    This dialog is the on that pops up after executing tool.
    Crash
    Crash dialog that appears after some exception is thrown.
    GoToLine
    This is GoToLine dialog, which we know from many text editors out there, that is jumping to selected line in textPane, which we reference using internal MainFrame instance.
    MainFrame
    Main frame for MEdit project.
    SearchWindow
    This window is reproducing look of Windows search form.
    Start
    Main class for MEdit project.
